---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import risultati from '../../../assets/photos/odontoriatria1.webp';

const calendlyUrl = 'https://app.reclaim.ai/m/davide-veneto/call-conoscitiva';
---

<Layout
	lang="en"
	title="245 qualified leads at 1.47 each | Davide Veneto"
	description="How we generated 245 qualified leads at 1.47 each for a dental equipment company using a webinar on subsidized financing."
>
	<section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-28 relative">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<a href="/en/" class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 inline-block hover:text-red-glow transition-colors">&larr; BACK TO HOME</a>
			<p class="text-red font-heading text-lg tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">DENTAL EQUIPMENT</p>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading leading-[0.95] mb-6">
				245 qualified leads<br />
				<span class="text-red">at 1.47 each</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
				How we generated hundreds of qualified contacts for a Top 3 dental equipment company using a webinar on government-subsidized financing.
			</p>
			<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mt-8"></div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-black-light border-t border-b border-white/5">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The context</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
				<p>My client sells equipment in the dental market. They are one of the Top 3 competitors. Price is often the deciding factor.</p>
				<div class="p-6 bg-black-card border border-red/20">
					<p class="text-white font-semibold">Either you differentiate through the service you offer, or you end up in a race to the bottom.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The idea — <span class="text-red">Government grants partnership</span></h2>
			<div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
				<p>We searched for companies that manage regional grants. We found a few, formed a partnership, and created a webinar program on subsidized financing.</p>
				<p>The words "Subsidized Financing" only evoke boredom. We needed a way to make it less dull and more appealing.</p>
				<div class="p-6 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50 mt-8">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-3">THE TITLE THAT WORKED</p>
					<p class="text-white text-xl italic">"How to purchase new equipment without touching your cash flow, thanks to government incentives"</p>
					<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3">vs. "Free Webinar" — 0 benefits, 0 identification, 0 appeal.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-black-light border-t border-b border-white/5">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The <span class="text-red">funnel</span></h2>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-stretch">
				<div class="flex-1 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50 text-center">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-lg mb-1">STEP 1</p>
					<p class="text-white">Meta Ads</p>
				</div>
				<div class="hidden sm:flex items-center text-red font-heading text-2xl">&rarr;</div>
				<div class="flex-1 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50 text-center">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-lg mb-1">STEP 2</p>
					<p class="text-white">Registration page</p>
				</div>
				<div class="hidden sm:flex items-center text-red font-heading text-2xl">&rarr;</div>
				<div class="flex-1 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50 text-center">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-lg mb-1">STEP 3</p>
					<p class="text-white">Webinar</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-8">
				<p>Registrants received an email sequence to ensure they showed up to the webinar.</p>
				<p>After the webinar, attendees were called to offer a free consultation.</p>
				<p class="text-white font-semibold">The webinar was structured as: Target's problems &rarr; Solution &rarr; Why choose us (and why consultation spots were limited).</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The <span class="text-red">results</span></h2>
			<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
				<div class="p-6 bg-red/10 border border-red/30 text-center">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-4xl mb-2">245</p>
					<p class="text-white">Qualified leads</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 bg-red/10 border border-red/30 text-center">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-4xl mb-2">1.47</p>
					<p class="text-white">Cost per lead</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 bg-red/10 border border-red/30 text-center">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-4xl mb-2">43%</p>
					<p class="text-white">Show-up rate</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="p-6 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50 mt-6">
				<p class="text-white text-lg">After the first email: <span class="text-red font-semibold">10 consultation calls</span> on grants.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mt-8">
				<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-3">DASHBOARD DATA</p>
				<img src={(risultati as any).src ?? risultati} alt="245 contacts on Facebook at 1.47" class="w-full rounded border border-gray-700/50" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-red relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative">
			<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-white/30 mb-8 mx-auto"></div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading mb-6 text-white">Want similar results<br />for your business?</h2>
			<p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10">Book a free 30-minute call. Let's analyze your situation together.</p>
			<a href={calendlyUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary-inverted">Book a strategy call</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="py-8 border-t border-gray-700/30">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Power Adv di Veneto Davide. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>
